<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234663>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6 – 11. Anoplodactylus mirim (UFPB. PYC – 085). Male. Habitus: 6, dorsal; 7, lateral; 8, ventral proboscis; 9, chela; 10, oviger; 11, 3 rd leg. Scale bar: Figs. 6 – 8, 0.05 mm; Fig. 9, 0.025 mm; Figs. 10 – 11, 0.05 mm, details of Fig. 11, 0.025 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234663/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

